{"desi_lesson":{"title":"Basic Verbs: To Be & Common Actions","target_language":"Kannada","theme":"Basic Verbs: To Be & Common Actions","vocabulary":[{"english":"I am","target_language_script":"ನಾನು ಇದ್ದೇನೆ","transliteration":"nānu iddēne","pronunciation":"nah-noo id-day-nay"},{"english":"you are","target_language_script":"ನೀವು ಇದ್ದೀರಿ","transliteration":"nīvu iddīri","pronunciation":"nee-voo id-dee-ree"},{"english":"he/she/it is","target_language_script":"ಅವನು/ಅವಳು/ಅದು ಇದೆ","transliteration":"avanu/avaļu/adu ide","pronunciation":"uh-vuh-noo/uh-vuh-loo/uh-doo ee-day"},{"english":"we are","target_language_script":"ನಾವು ಇದ್ದೇವೆ","transliteration":"nāvu iddēve","pronunciation":"nah-voo id-day-vay"},{"english":"you all are","target_language_script":"ನೀವು ಇದ್ದೀರಿ","transliteration":"nīvu iddīri","pronunciation":"nee-voo id-dee-ree"},{"english":"they are","target_language_script":"ಅವರು ಇದ್ದಾರೆ","transliteration":"avaru iddāre","pronunciation":"uh-vuh-roo id-dah-ray"},{"english":"to eat","target_language_script":"ತಿನ್ನಲು","transliteration":"tinnalu","pronunciation":"tin-nuh-loo"},{"english":"to drink","target_language_script":"ಕುಡಿಯಲು","transliteration":"kuḍiyalu","pronunciation":"koo-dee-yah-loo"},{"english":"to sleep","target_language_script":"ನಿದ್ರೆ ಮಾಡಲು","transliteration":"nidre māḍalu","pronunciation":"nid-ray mah-dah-loo"},{"english":"to see","target_language_script":"ನೋಡಲು","transliteration":"nōḍalu","pronunciation":"noh-dah-loo"}],"example_sentences":[{"english":"I am eating.","target_language_script":"ನಾನು ತಿನ್ನುತ್ತಿದ್ದೇನೆ","transliteration":"nānu tinnuttiddēne","pronunciation":"nah-noo tin-noo-tid-day-nay"},{"english":"You are drinking water.","target_language_script":"ನೀವು ನೀರು ಕುಡಿಯುತ್ತಿದ್ದೀರಿ","transliteration":"nīvu nīru kuḍiyuttiddiri","pronunciation":"nee-voo nee-roo koo-dee-yoo-tid-dee-ree"},{"english":"He is sleeping.","target_language_script":"ಅವನು ನಿದ್ರೆ ಮಾಡುತ್ತಿದ್ದಾನೆ","transliteration":"avanu nidre māḍuttidāne","pronunciation":"uh-vuh-noo nid-ray ma